FOR USE WITH ELLUCIAN EEDM
Retrieves an address type by GUID.
/// Unique ID representing the Address Type to get An AddressType object.

member.exception:
Thrown if the personId or communication code properties of the input object are null, empty,
            if the correspondence request cannot be updated due to a record lock, 
            or if the user does not have access to the person's correspondence requests

